info.name: Easy Coffee Box of 5 - Vienna Roast
info.description: Serves 1 | Start your day with the deep, rich flavor of our Vienna Roast Coffee. This dark roast strikes the perfect balance between smooth and bold, giving you just the right kick to tackle whatever comes your way. Enjoy the cozy notes of chocolate and caramel in every sip, making your morning coffee a delightful and energizing experience. Wake up, feel great, and power through your day with Vienna Roast Easy Coffee!

info.name: Easy Coffee Box of 5 - SO Medium Light Roast

We traveled far and wide to find the perfect beans, ensuring top quality and unique flavors. Each bean is roasted to perfection to bring out its balanced, fruity nuances. Enjoy a cup that's as special as you are, and start your morning with a delightful boost of pure coffee happiness!

info.name: Easy Coffee Box of 5 - Monsoon Malabar

Each cup is packed with bold flavours, complemented by strong, nutty, earthy notes. Sip on this for a perfectly versatile cup that can be enjoyed any time of the day. Our suggestion? Keep a second Easy Coffee Bag of our Monsoon Malabar coffee handy because you’ll definitely want more!
